  <p class="text-center text-muted">A wild journey from "meh" to "let’s GO!" 🧭</p>

  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e" alt="Adventure Image" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" />
