    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>So... what's TripTribe?</h3>
      <p>
        TripTribe started with one goal: <strong>to make travel planning less painful</strong> than a group project in college.
        We were tired of chaotic WhatsApp groups, lost screenshots, and that one friend who never replies. So, we created a space where travelers
        can connect, plan, and explore — without losing their minds (or their socks).
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're a solo adventurer, a "let's plan a Goa trip for the 47th time" dreamer, or someone who just wants to find a tribe to vibe with —
        TripTribe is for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
