      <h3>Meet the Tribe Behind TripTribe 🧠❤️</h3>
      <p>
        We’re a group of caffeine-fueled developers, designers, and meme lords who believe that travel is better when it’s shared (and when the
        Wi-Fi works). Our team includes:
