      <ul>
        <li>🚀 Coders who write more bugs than code (but fix them eventually)</li>
        <li>🎨 Designers who argue about font sizes at 2am</li>
        <li>📢 Marketers who think hashtags solve everything</li>
        <li>🍕 A guy who only joined for the snacks</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

